<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <title>ورود</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/128/3304/3304749.png" type="image/x-icon">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/remixicon/fonts/remixicon.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/toastify-js/src/toastify.min.css">
    <script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/toastify-js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/axios/1.7.2/axios.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/toastify.css">
    <style>
        .toggle-password {
            cursor: pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="flex items-center justify-center h-screen">
    <div id="first-auth" class="w-full max-w-lg">
        <form class="bg-white border rounded-md px-10 pt-6 pb-8 mb-4" action="javascript:void(0);">
            <h1 class="text-center mt-4 text-2xl font-bold">ثبت نام</h1>
            <h1 class="text-center mb-10 mt-4 text-gray-700">برای ادامه شماره موبایل خود را وارد کنید.</h1>
            <div class="mb-6">
                <label class="block text-gray-700 font-bold mb-2" for="phone">
                    شماره تلفن
                </label>
                <input
                    class="appearance-none border rounded w-full py-4 px-4 text-gray-700 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline"
                    id="phone" type="text" placeholder="شماره تلفن">
            </div>
            <div class="mb-6 relative">
                <label class="block text-gray-700 font-bold mb-2" for="password">
                    پسورد
                </label>
                <input
                    class="appearance-none border rounded w-full py-4 px-4 text-gray-700 mb-3 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline"
                    id="password" type="password" placeholder="********">

                <i id="eye-open"
                    class="ri-eye-line absolute text-xl  inset-y-0 left-0 top-4 flex items-center px-4 text-gray-700 toggle-password hidden"></i>
                <i id="eye-closed"
                    class="ri-eye-off-line absolute text-xl inset-y-0 left-0 top-4 flex items-center px-4 text-gray-700 toggle-password "></i>
            </div>
            <span class="text-gray-700 text-center text-sm"><i class="ri-error-warning-line text-xl"></i> استفاده از
                سفیر به معنی پذیرش قوانین و مقررات این سرویس است.</span>

            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mt-6 mb-4 w-full">
                <button
                    class="bg-blue-500 w-full border-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white text-xl font-bold py-4 px-4 rounded focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline"
                    type="button" id="register-btn">
                    ثبت نام
                </button>
            </div>
          <span class="mt-4 text-center"> حساب دارید؟ <a class="text-blue-600" href="/login">ورود</a></span>
        </form>
    </div>

    <div id="second-auth" dir="ltr" class="bg-white py-16 px-12 rounded-lg border w-full max-w-lg hidden">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-2 text-center">کد تایید را وارد کنید </h2>
        <p class="mb-8 text-center text-gray-600">کد ۵ رقمی به شماره 09383901146 ارسال شد</p>
        <form>
            <div class="flex justify-between mb-4 w-full">
                <input id="inpt-1" type="text" maxlength="1" class="w-16 mr-2 h-16 pl-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-yellow-200" oninput="this.value=this.value.replace(/[^0-9]/g,'');">
                <input id="inpt-2" type="text" maxlength="1" class="w-16 mr-2 h-16 pl-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-yellow-200" oninput="this.value=this.value.replace(/[^0-9]/g,'');">
                <input id="inpt-3" type="text" maxlength="1" class="w-16 mr-2 h-16 pl-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-yellow-200" oninput="this.value=this.value.replace(/[^0-9]/g,'');">
                <input id="inpt-4" type="text" maxlength="1" class="w-16 mr-2 h-16 pl-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-yellow-200" oninput="this.value=this.value.replace(/[^0-9]/g,'');">
                <input id="inpt-5" type="text" maxlength="1" class="w-16 mr-2 h-16 pl-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-yellow-200" oninput="this.value=this.value.replace(/[^0-9]/g,'');">
            </div>
            <div id="timer" class="text-gray-600 text-center"></div>
            <button id="verify-btn" type="button" class="w-full text-xl bg-blue-500 text-white py-4 mt-6 rounded-md hover:bg-blue-600 transition duration-200">تایید و ادامه</button>
        </form>
    </div>
 
    <script src="../../javascripts/user/register.js"></script>
    <script src="../../javascripts/user/verify.js"></script>
    <script src="../../javascripts/utils/toast.js"></script>
</body>

</html>